64
00:03:43,270 --> 00:03:45,460
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">A filthy impostor!</font>

65
00:03:45,460 --> 00:03:48,780
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Do you think God will forgive this, Coribou?!</font>

66
00:03:48,780 --> 00:03:50,310
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Dig!  Dig!</font>

67
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:53,480
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Indeed, my friends!  Let's bury 'em all!</font>

68
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:55,910
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Oh, God!</font>

69
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:59,680
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I will bury these imbeciles!</font>

