What could we have done against him?</font>

76
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:26,380
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The only ones that escaped from the plaza were the Caribou brothers with their crew...</font>

77
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:29,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">and a few members of the fake Straw Hat Pirates.</font>

78
00:04:29,950 --> 00:04:31,950
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We captured everyone else,</font>

79
00:04:31,950 --> 00:04:36,810
