84
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:57,520
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Send word to Navy HQ in the New World.</font>

85
00:04:57,520 --> 00:05:01,880
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The Straw Hat Pirates have completely recovered.</font>

86
00:05:06,740 --> 00:05:09,280
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">They're gone in the blink of an eye.</font>

87
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:13,460
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Monkey-chan and the rest sure have become tough.</font>

88
00:05:13,460 --> 00:05:15,080
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">You were watching?</font>

89
00:05:15,080 --> 00:05:16,630
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Of course.  I am a fan, after all.</font>

90
00:05:17,410 --> 00:05:20,970
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Are you remembering something, Ray-san?</font>

91
