00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:35,350
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>It's Rayleigh.</i></font>

96
00:05:36,420 --> 00:05:41,320
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>I'm Roger!  Our meeting here is destiny, Rayleigh!</i></font>

97
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:44,760
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Wanna come with me and turn the world on its head?</i></font>

98
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:47,570
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>The world?</i></font>

