<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Is the water really not gonna come in?  I'm worried!</font>

111
00:06:32,050 --> 00:06:35,790
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It feels like we're drifting away from the human world!  I'm tense.</font>

112
00:06:35,790 --> 00:06:40,760
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">A-Are we gonna be able to return to the surface?</font>

113
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,510
