<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Yeah, 'cause you got on the wrong ship!</i></font>

121
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:08,270
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Shut up!  Let us be in awe here!</i></font>

122
00:07:09,090 --> 00:07:12,740
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I can hardly believe that the roots
stretch all the way to the ocean floor.</font>

123
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:15,610
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">They're so big, I'm speechless.</font>

124
