125
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:23,940
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>It's humongous!</i></font>

126
00:07:23,940 --> 00:07:27,570
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm so excited!  An adventure beneath the sea!</font>

127
00:07:27,570 --> 00:07:29,420
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's like a dream!</font>

