132
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:43,450
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What if the soap bubble breaks?!</font>

133
00:07:43,450 --> 00:07:45,450
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I'm gonna kill you if you do that again!</font>

134
00:07:45,450 --> 00:07:49,170
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Nami-san, before these two do something else stupid,</font>

135
00:07:49,170 --> 00:07:50,960
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">could you tell us how this coating works?</font>

136
00:07:51,470 --> 00:07:53,100
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I guess so, Sanji-kun.</font>

137
00:07:53,100 --> 00:07:55,670
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Rayleigh-san gave me some notes, after all.</font>

138
00:07:55,670 --> 00:07:57,740
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">So, let me explain it to you all.</font>

139
00:07:57,740 --> 00:08:00,840
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">She moved!  A real life beauty!</font>

140
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:02,390
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Sanji!</i></font>

141
00:08:02,390 --> 00:08:03,690
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's breaking!  Breaking!  Breaking!</font>

142
00:08:03,690 --> 00:08:06,340
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Just how far can you be propelled by a nosebleed?!</font>

143
00:08:08,610 --> 00:08:10,780
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Sanji got thrown into the sea!</font>

144
00:08:10,780 --> 00:08:12,370
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Sanji!</i></font>

145
00:08:12,370 --> 00:08:14,970
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Come back!</i></font>

146
00:08:15,970 --> 00:08:17,390
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The ocean!  My strength is fading...</font>

147
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:20,210
<font face="Impress BT" size="55"><i>Hang in there!</i></font>

148
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:24,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">What happened to you, Sanji?!</font>

149
00:08:24,890 --> 00:08:28,090
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">It's like you've developed
a crippling weakness to women!</font>

150
00:08:28,090 --> 00:08:29,690
