154
00:08:40,430 --> 00:08:43,160
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">he might die from blood loss.</font>

155
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:46,500
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">We'll have to get
a blood transfusion for him on Fishman Island.</font>

156
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:50,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I wonder if fishmen and mermen have the same blood types as humans.</font>

157
00:08:50,750 --> 00:08:52,840
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">So basically, like we just saw,</font>

158
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:59,890
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">the soap-bubble surrounding this ship has the same properties as the ones on the Sabaody Archipelago?</font>

159
00:08:59,890 --> 00:09:03,240
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Don't just calmly continue your analysis of soap-bubbles!</font>

160
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,000
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Indeed.</font>

161
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:06,130
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Fundamentally, they're the same.</font>

162
00:09:06,130 --> 00:09:09,750
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">They'll stretch to a certain extent,
and after that, you'll pierce through them.</font>

